Class MetaDataUtils

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.mosip.kernel.masterdata.utils.MetaDataUtils

  • @Component
public class MetaDataUtils
extends java.lang.Object
    MetaDataUtils class provide methods to copy values from DTO to entity along with that it create some meta data which is required before an entity to be saved into database.
